      "content": "Interesting. When you mention \"rapidly changing demographics\" in Area B as a factor for potential value decreases, are you implying that shifts in the racial or cultural makeup of a neighborhood tend to negatively impact market stability? How much weight should an analyst give to demographic shifts when assessing risk?",
